---
title: Sweet Italian Sausage with Couscous and Spinach
description: Italian sausage has an established place on pastas and pizza pies, which is why we’re trying something different and adding it to bouncy couscous. The adventuresome combo, which is rounded out by supple mushrooms and tender spinach, is a textural treat and packs plenty of garlicky flavor, too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-italian-sausages-with-freg-4b71ee76.jpg
